replies.body:
You know who else hasn't gotten a skin since their release?

{{champion:83}} 

Wait for your rework, then wait some more, *then* if you're lucky you'll get a skin!

{{champion:6}} {{champion:83}} {{champion:69}} 

Zac has a whole other level to get on before I feel any sort of bad for him. 

And those are ignoring the champions that still only have skins from a long time ago and then several years of interim before a more recent one, like Rammus and Shyvana. Some champions have gone for longer than Zac's existence without before getting a new skin.
